Package: metplot
Type: Package
Title: Plotting of meteorological data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Roman Attinger
Maintainer: Roman Attinger <roman.attinger@env.ethz.ch>
Description: This package provides various plotting routines for quick and easy
    plotting of meteorological data from numerical weather prediction and climate models.
    Besides regular lat-lon maps it is also possible to plot time-series of
    meteorological data and much more :)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    raster,
    ncdf4,
    rnaturalearth,
    ggspatial,
    sp,
    maptools,
    rgeos,
    RColorBrewer,
    fields
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
